short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helps you stay informed about surcharges at restaurants and bars in the DC, Maryland, and Virginia area.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TransparentFee DMV is designed to help you stay informed about surcharges at your favorite restaurants and bars in the DC, Maryland, and Virginia (DMV) area. With the rising popularity of service fees and surcharges, it's more important than ever to know what you're paying for.
